latestPosts.caption:
i had the most beautiful time at my friend @rashmify’s event where she launched her brand @thankjade 💚
it’s rare to come across something so unique and rooted in intention. every piece in the collection is made with 100% authentic jade, not the mixed, commercial versions we often see, but real, unaltered jade in its purest form.

from beauty tools and intricate jewellery to buttons, tiles, and other decor elements.. this brand is reimagining jade in ways we’ve never seen before.
it’s fresh, it’s luxurious, and it’s deeply thoughtful.

so proud of her for building something that feels timeless, modern, and rich with cultural value 💚
